Afro Genie Lyric Licensing, Sourcing & Compliance Framework
Legal, Product & Artist Verification Roadmap (2025)
1. Introduction
Afro Genie is building Africa’s first AI-powered lyric translation and cultural annotation platform, translating local languages and dialects into global ones while preserving meaning, context, and cultural ownership.

To operate legally and sustainably, Afro Genie ensures that all lyrics hosted, translated, or displayed are properly licensed or self-verified by artists.


This document outlines the legal, licensing, and compliance architecture that underpins this mission.
